2021年2月7日，印度[[北阿坎德邦|北阿坎德邦]][[杰莫利县|杰莫利县]][[焦希默特|焦希默特]][[楠达德维山|楠达德维山]]谷發生[[冰湖溃决洪水|'''冰湖溃决洪水''']]（亦有媒體報道為冰川斷裂並墜落至[[道里根加河|道里根加河]]引發洪水），导致[[阿勒格嫩達河|阿勒格嫩達河]]和[[道里根加河_(西)|道里根加河]]沿岸发生大规模洪水，影响面积约14平方公里<ref name=32人>{{cite news |title=印度北部冰川断裂致死人数升至32人 |url=https://news.sina.com.cn/w/2021-02-10/doc-ikftssap5091033.shtml |accessdate=2021-02-10 |archive-date=2021-03-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210317013818/https://news.sina.com.cn/w/2021-02-10/doc-ikftssap5091033.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Uttarakhand news live: Glacier bursts in Uttarakhand's Chamoli district|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/breaking-news-live-updates-07-02-2021/liveblog/80730052.cms|accessdate=2021-02-07|work=The Times of India|language=en|archive-date=2021-02-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210207073419/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/breaking-news-live-updates-07-02-2021/liveblog/80730052.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Glacier bursts in Uttarakhand's Chamoli district, causing flash flood in Dhauliganga: Highlights - Times of India|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/uttarakhand-glacier-burst-in-chamoli-damages-hydropower-plant-rescue-operations-underway/articleshow/80732809.cms|accessdate=2021-02-07|work=The Times of India|language=en|archive-date=2021-02-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210207073327/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/uttarakhand-glacier-burst-in-chamoli-damages-hydropower-plant-rescue-operations-underway/articleshow/80732809.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref>。洪水冲毁了一座水电站和河岸边的部分房屋<ref>{{Cite web|title=印度北部冰川断裂致上百人失踪|url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/2021-02/07/c_1127077129.htm|accessdate=|author=|date=|format=|publisher=|language=|archive-date=2021-03-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210316125130/http://www.xinhuanet.com/2021-02/07/c_1127077129.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，上百名在附近施工的工人和居民失踪<ref>{{Cite web|title=Uttarakhand glacier burst: Over 100 missing, power plant damaged in Chamoli|url=https://scroll.in/latest/986187/uttarakhand-glacier-burst-over-100-missing-power-plant-damaged-in-chamoli|accessdate=2021-02-07|author=Staff|first=Scroll|work=Scroll.in|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210209113300/https://scroll.in/latest/986187/uttarakhand-glacier-burst-over-100-missing-power-plant-damaged-in-chamoli|dead-url=no}}</ref>。事故發生時的[[北阿坎德邦|北阿坎德邦]]冬季的降雪量减少使得[[冰川|冰川]]未能及時修復是造成此次灾害的原因之一<ref>{{Cite web|title=Glacier breaks in Chamoli, experts blame low snowfall|url=https://www.downtoearth.org.in/news/natural-disasters/glacier-breaks-in-chamoli-experts-blame-low-snowfall-75417|access-date=2021-02-07|website=www.downtoearth.org.in|language=en|archive-date=2021-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210209113301/https://www.downtoearth.org.in/news/natural-disasters/glacier-breaks-in-chamoli-experts-blame-low-snowfall-75417|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|date=2021-02-07|title=India floods: Scores missing after glacier smashes Uttarakhand dam|language=en-GB|work=BBC News|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-india-55969669|access-date=2021-02-07|archive-date=2021-02-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210207100607/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-india-55969669|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

